  <summary date="2021-05-18T14:04:44Z" status="Introduced in House">Pre-Apprenticeships To Hardhats Act or the PATH Act

This bill directs the Department of Labor to provide grants to eligible entities to develop pre-apprenticeship programs in the building and construction trades that serve underrepresented populations, including individuals from low income and rural census tracts.</summary>
